==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Jonah
<hw>Jo"nah</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The Hebrew prophet, who
was cast overboard as one who endangered the ship; hence, any person
whose presence is unpropitious.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Jonah crab</b></col> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>, <cd>a large crab
(<spn>Cancer borealis</spn>) of the eastern coast of the United States,
sometimes found between tides, but usually in deep water.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Jonesian</ent>⟦br⟧
